{"tid":750080,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【公諸同好】露肩女車廂睇 AV 網民：女人都可以咸濕","createTime":"2018-07-20T14:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T17:23:18.000Z","uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"61a9a470d9f1ebd21ff47d46e11857565e7da2d3","tid":750080,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/07/16/8/88e70ec158d0bb65b43ec80339fea963.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F8%2F88e70ec158d0bb65b43ec80339fea963.jpg&h=d9188741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「男人 = 咸濕」這個等式仿佛已經成為恆久不變的真理，今日小編並不打算與大家討論是否真的所有男人都是咸濕，而是當我們指出男人都是咸濕的時候，有沒有想過其實咸濕並不是男人的專利，女人一樣可以好咸濕？<br />\n<br />\n日前有網民於 Facebook 群組「 PLAY HARD 玩硬」分享一段影片，一名身穿白色露肩上衣的女子，在公共交通工具車廂中觀看影片，細心一看，便會發現她看的並不是一般的韓劇或日劇等，而是含有裸露鏡頭的色情影片。對於有妙齡女子公然在車上觀看色情電影，發帖者慨嘆「世風日下」。<br />\n<br />\n影片引起網民熱烈討論，不過大部份網民對於有女性看成人電影並不感到意外，直言「女人都可以咸濕」，亦有人反斥拍片者的偷拍行為可惡。<br />\n<br />\n此外，亦有網民猜測有關影片可能是涉事女子的朋友於通訊群組中互傳，並不是有心在公眾場觀看色情影片。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=10&amp;v=aTxDeT3g9zA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D10%26v%3DaTxDeT3g9zA&d=2Ff9JbElw05XPoJfiLQ2XttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7d42953f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=10&amp;v=aTxDeT3g9zA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180716/1/67/1/%E5%85%AC%E8%AB%B8%E5%90%8C%E5%A5%BD-%E9%9C%B2%E8%82%A9%E5%A5%B3%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E7%9D%87-AV-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%92%B8%E6%BF%95-9033272.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180716%2F1%2F67%2F1%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%25AB%25B8%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25A5%25BD-%25E9%259C%25B2%25E8%2582%25A9%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BB%2582%25E7%259D%2587-AV-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2583